Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.11,0:00:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配備著以電腦為導航系統的賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「CYBER F0RMULA」正式登場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.39,0:00:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替「F-l」的2l世紀賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.17,0:00:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令全世界人都狂熱起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,,新世紀GPX 「CYBER F0RMULA」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:33.55,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快出發 不用有任何擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.56,0:00:40.09,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你 因為喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.98,0:00:43.72,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:47.49,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自你求助的訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.73,0:00:53.60,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨夜開始一直感覺得到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.62,0:01:00.08,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突如其來的風暴阻擋了前進的路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:04.04,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望便浮現在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.09,0:01:08.95,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喜歡 是奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:15.00,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會放在心上 不論什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:20.75,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的波浪會緊隨而來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.23,0:01:27.79,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在馬上出發 決不動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.80,0:01:33.58,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現夢想 永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.58,0:01:36.73,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:43.74,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快出發 不用有任何擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:50.45,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你 因為喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正當隼人逐漸從世界錦標賽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一戰的失敗陰影中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走出來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加賀出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他邀請隼人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.43,0:02:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加危險之旅的車賽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.33,0:02:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一場由一群
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將生命置之度外的賽車手們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這場沒有比賽規則的戰鬥中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.94,0:02:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人從加賀身上學到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.21,0:02:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己所欠缺的見機行事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈機應變的本領
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽車就是戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一場你死我活的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十四話 青春的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個被稱炒蝎了的溫床的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘魯玻利維亞高原的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山嶽跑道上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭 積奇 羅比等好手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:02:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陸續的飛馳而過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而今年首次登場的卡門
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也緊跟在後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡門的車子打轉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說要是不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踩到蝎子的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,則有可能招致死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡門就像中了這道詛咒一般
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喪生在這高原上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 照這種情形看來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達有必要做改良
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.87,0:03:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 這樣更可以展現一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們維修人員的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.44,0:03:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔 我們已經
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看完去年的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想著手進行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達的改良工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改良
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次的比賽場地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在秘魯的高原上舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是以山嶽道路為主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在高四千公尺的高原上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空氣也非常稀薄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達必須針對特性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做必要的改良
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 這次的改良
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會讓你刮目相看的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等著瞧好了 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美樹跟良平顯得非常的謹慎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的比賽場地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎非常的困難
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 怎麼可以在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽前就洩我的氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入莫斯科國境後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要先試跑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽跟比賽之間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不容許選手有喘息的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在管生阿斯拉達車隊一行人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正朝著世界盃錦標賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二次決賽的舞台秘魯前進
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.86,0:04:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過改良後的阿斯拉達
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將可應付秘魯的山嶽跑道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的阿斯拉達重量比以前重一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:05:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是車體的平衡性並未改變
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再給我一點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整理當地的資料好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不急著用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多花點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把資料準備齊全就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備測試了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 開起來的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車身真的加重了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這並不會影響到駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改裝後的我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了重生的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到你會說這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上坡左彎道 要注意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 引擎也沒有事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現標高是二千八百公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我準備再往上開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好體驗一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太勉強哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對面有急駛而來的車輛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我是避開了貨車
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是卻撞上了僊人掌了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小心一點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:05:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個地方空氣乾燥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面非常堅硬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞上可不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩翼稍微歪了 調整一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大約向左0.2公分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉快好了 大家來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美樹 先吃飯吧 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等一下再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那我們先去吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.62,0:06:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 你也去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蟲 光是這些小蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就足以破壞車子的平衡性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.87,0:06:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這肉燒的不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看誰做的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼簡單誰不會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 我不給你吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偏要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良平 你吃那麼多肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對身體不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快喝點水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次別吃那麼快了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我不吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飽了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看螺絲有沒有栓緊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良平好像很重視這次比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.83,0:07:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次的決賽他無法參加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了補償上次的缺席
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經栓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正閒著也是閒著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便換換大燈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.85,0:07:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上的星星好漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像快要掉下來的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸媽絕對不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞞不了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你臉上的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你在想什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第二次的決戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論如何我都要贏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸媽看到新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會來看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要贏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直線前進安定性優良
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著我要測試
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉彎的特性了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎會這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達 你查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.68,0:08:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方向盤失控的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在硬體機能及軟體方面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有異常現象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是的確有向外偏的現象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在轉彎的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.93,0:08:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻都是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右轉的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻有向外偏的不平衡現象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是外在因素
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道會是風
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:08:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 只要我再繞回去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以知道是不是風了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右轉的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是會有不平衡現象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但原因卻不在風
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有異常現象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了安全起見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更換一些重要零件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方向盤油 機油幫涌\N還有方向盤軸 懸吊桿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前為止 沒有任何的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經都過了三個小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子沒有異常現象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用電腦檢查的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,程式的方向也完全正常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我在右轉的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確產生了一種
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不平衡的現象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我真的察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:09:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是不車子的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.97,0:10:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能夠保證
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的判斷就正確嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們檢查過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.51,0:10:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有可能產生問題的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前為止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒有發生過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右轉的時候不平衡現象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我敢說這一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整備上的失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經把全部精力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在車子的整備上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個小小的賽車手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有資格批評
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個都住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵吵鬧鬧的太不像話了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔 我還要試一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩隻手固定在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方向盤的正中央
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到右轉彎道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有找到真正原因之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要查明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是我的技術有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是另有原因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是方向盤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向外偏的不平衡現象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測定器上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有任何異常現象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我每一次右轉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:10:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會有不平衡的現象出現
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是阿斯拉達
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次有這種現象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要老把原因歸罪於機器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看是你駕駛技術有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.80,0:11:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面有障礙物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.94,0:11:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.23,0:11:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.02,0:12:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些車子的哭泣聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏好像是車子的墳墓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果車子真有問題的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我跟阿斯拉達都將有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葬身在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那如果是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車手本身的技術有問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自信心雖然是重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不可能是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我也遇過同樣的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算起來已經是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三十年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時隼人的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.52,0:12:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香的爸爸還有我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是高中三年級的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們車子已經設計出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是廣之設計的籃圖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我們監定一下 拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還不夠成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我要開始工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 今天不幫忙了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我馬上開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我去幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都願意做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等將來時機成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我們利用這裏的廢鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作屬於我們自己的車子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把那邊的東西整理一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時我們雖然很窮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但擁有一個製造一輛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屬於自己車子的美麗夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一遍又一遍的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修改設計圖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.87,0:14:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並請源叔不斷給我們指導
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日子一天天的過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們卻得不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾是F1賽車維修員
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.54,0:14:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源叔的點頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個設計圖太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這部車子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會 跑得很快的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見 你成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.23,0:14:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連源叔都稱讚你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.47,0:14:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在源叔的同意下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源叔工廠裏面的廢鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作我們期待已久的車子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於乘載著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們三個年青人夢想的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:14:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘風一號誕生了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一輛屬於我們的車子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過了無數次的測試
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在參加
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FJl600比賽前的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後測試中…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,營生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.52,0:15:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.46,0:15:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是車子歪七扭八的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看是要報銷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因在於你整備上的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在撞車之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縣吊繫統就已經發生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,異常的現象了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然敢批評我的整備功力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次在出車之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.24,0:15:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都做了徹底的安全檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為問題出在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的操縱失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的操縱技術有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在整備上盡了全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該負起撞車的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:15:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想平白無故的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死在你過剩的自信心下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可惡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我們將乘風一號
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全分解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細檢查可能的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是找不到任何的缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說失誤真的在我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.35,0:16:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差動齒輪可能有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏竟然會有小石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是更換齒輪油時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心掉進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當時嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於自己的不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點就害死了我最要好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.27,0:16:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管生 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.98,0:16:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:16:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起 我發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不碰任何的車子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是不幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就沒辦法實現
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當一個賽車手的夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維修人員到處都找得到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正沒辦法再繼續下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鐵 小鐵等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就承認自己被打敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果扼殺了好朋友的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後怎麼面對你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在以前 我曾經因為
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:17:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整備上的失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而害死了我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從此以後我開始用放大鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來調查車輛發生事故的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在每當我在修車的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總彷彿聽到車子的嘆息聲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為它們大部份是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛人的橫衝直撞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是不愛惜而被撞毀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.06,0:18:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是整備上的失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不需要這個放大鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鐵 這個我送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會好好保存好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一直保存至今
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔 請把它借給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:18:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果檢查結果不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維修整備上的失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:18:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你得向他們道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方向盤部位無異常現象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢查縣吊繫統
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從感應系統到齒輪為止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.68,0:19:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一個零件每一顆螺絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能夠拆下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都得拆下來檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要徹底的調查真正原因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經五個小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道問題真的出在我身上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是我的問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,視力無問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是條纖維 糟丁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.67,0:20:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.03,0:20:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良平
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美樹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現答案了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔 原因出在扭力的分裂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.15,0:20:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在G感應器的雷射發射鏡片上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.69,0:20:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了髒東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼小的一個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連電腦都沒有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測出的微小東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會有如此大的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呀 只要有異物在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.23,0:20:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭力的前後分配就失去均衡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而使車子產生了不平衡的現象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們維修人員的失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我住口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為維護人員隊長的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該負起全部的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美樹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.52,0:21:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是隊長的錯 要怪就怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣嘛 美樹 良平
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們快點起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就麻煩你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再做一次車輛整備工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.51,0:21:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的性命就交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.29,0:21:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到這個情形
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.86,0:21:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.89,0:21:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是同一個隊伍的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.13,0:21:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團隊的精神不是隊員們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相處融洽就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.23,0:21:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是要彼此為保護
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方的生命而奮鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.67,0:21:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你們能夠發揮團隊精神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好打贏秘魯這一仗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天一早就要出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.18,0:21:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家趕快去準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:21:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:16.85,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他人目光沒有在背後注視著我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.45,0:22:23.56,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面向前方 生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:27.14,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為肩負著使命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:30.28,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互信任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.30,0:22:37.03,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下雙手 仰望天空時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.76,0:22:40.16,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互信任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.18,0:22:48.89,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑容是我心中的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.61,0:22:55.87,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有現在加倍努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:23:00.34,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能有明天的輝煌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:05.85,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 不用後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.87,0:23:11.51,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著自己樹立的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:16.23,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎著風前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:21.36,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終我們會是勝利者

